  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-title">Our Mission</span>
          <p>
            As renters, we understand the challenges of managing shared living expenses. Whether it's collecting rent from roommates, 
            splitting utility bills, or keeping track of who paid what, the process can be overwhelming - especially when one person 
            bears the responsibility of managing it all.
          </p>
          <p>
            SplitIt was created to solve these common pain points. Our platform empowers each tenant to take responsibility for their 
            share while making the entire process seamless and transparent.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-title">What We Offer</span>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 m6">
              <h5><i class="material-icons left">home</i>House Management</h5>
              <p>Create and manage your shared living space, add roommates, and set up recurring payments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m6">
              <h5><i class="material-icons left">account_balance</i>Bill Splitting</h5>
              <p>Easily split rent, utilities, and other shared expenses among housemates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12 m6">
              <h5><i class="material-icons left">payment</i>Venmo Integration</h5>
              <p>Secure and convenient payments through Venmo integration.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m6">
              <h5><i class="material-icons left">notifications</i>Payment Reminders</h5>
              <p>Automated reminders ensure everyone pays their share on time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-title">Why Choose SplitIt?</span>
          <p>
            SplitIt transforms the way roommates handle shared expenses. No more awkward conversations about money, no more chasing 
            down payments, and no more confusion about who owes what. Our platform provides:
          </p>
          <ul class="browser-default">
            <li>Transparent tracking of all shared expenses</li>
            <li>Equal distribution of financial responsibility</li>
            <li>Simplified payment processes</li>
            <li>Reduced tension between roommates</li>
            <li>Peace of mind for everyone involved</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
